item.title: Help on LinkSys!
item.dc:creator: @hybrent hybrent
item.description:
@hybrent wrote:

If your trying to get to your router to portforward then…Click start>Run>type cmd>once the black box opens type ipconfig>search the results for something that says “default gateway” Enter that in you address bar. It will open a log in screen. Username can be anything, but default is admin admin. Or admin then no pass. Once logged in you can portforward! (See a portforward guide)
